        <updateDate>2021-03-30T14:41:09Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p>This bill restricts eligibility for certain federal assistance benefits to U.S. citizens or nationals. This restriction applies to all means-tested benefits, other than tax benefits, and to benefits authorized under the Social Security Act.</p> <p>An individual must provide evidence of citizenship or nationality status and attest to that status when applying for these benefits.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
